n Technology Accessibility Act 2.0 Techniques  Illinois Center for Information Technology and Web Accessibility’s HTML Best Practices  Usability.gov has a wealth of information on the whole Web development process, including project management, usability testing, information architecture, design, content strategy, user experience, and more.               Resources and Tools    Back to main content           Non-HTML Content     Captioning at UIC    Microsoft Word    Microsoft PowerPoint    PDF Documents    Multimedia Formats      Online Resources    Tools    Captioning at UIC                  UIC Logo        Digital Accessibility Committee       Contact   Phone: (312) 413-0886  dag@listserv.uic.edu        Social Media Accounts            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 